<p>A <code>ContentsListItem</code> is a plain <code>&lt;li&gt;</code>
  wrapper that typically contains a <code>ContentsLink</code>.</p>

<p>When the item represents the reader's current page location
  (via scroll-spy or server-side resolution), set
  <code>current: true</code> so the list item gets
  <code>aria-current="location"</code>.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/contents-nav/">Contents Nav demo</a>
  for a composed example.</p>
